Title: Crusade
Plot: Vala Mal Doran makes contact with Stargate Command from the Ori home galaxy, and tells the story of her life undercover in a village of followers building the Ori's invasion fleet.
GuestStars: Claudia Black, Tim Guinee, Daniella Evangelista, Garry Chalk, Tamlyn Tomita, Michael Ironside, Alex Dafoe
